(18, 'Hotel Old Sarajevo', 'hotel-old-sarajevo', 38, 237, 'Hotel Old Sarajevo features elegant accommodation in the pedestrian zone of the old town of Sarajevo (Baščaršija). This heritage hotel perfectly combines traditional charm, modern design, and superior comfort. Ideal for sightseeing, the hotel is located in the culinary center of Sarajevo (Bravadžiluk street), only a 10-meter walk from the famous City Hall (Vijećnica) and popular souvenir street (Kazandžiluk). Completely smoke-free, the hotel has a beautiful lounge area and 8 superior rooms, each with its own bathroom and shower. Guests enjoy a delightful breakfast of local delicacies and healthy choices. Outstanding service makes for a lovely stay in the heart of old Sarajevo. <br/> <p><ul><li>8 rooms with individual temperature control, premium bedding, blackout curtains, walk-in rain showers, and smart TVs.</li><li>Free WiFi and high-speed Internet connection.</li><li>24-hour reception.</li><li>Check-in starting at 15.00, check-out until 11.00.</li><li>Breakfast from 07.00 to 10.00.</li><li>Lounge area open from 11.00 to 22.00.</li><li>Daily housekeeping.</li><li>Dry cleaning and laundry service.</li><li>Airport pick-up available upon request.</li><li>Valet parking around the corner upon request.</li><li>Baby cot available for free.</li><li>Children up to 11 years old stay free in their parents’ room, using existing beds and bedding. (Extra beds are not available.)</li><li><span>The hotel is completely non-smoking.</span></li></ul><br></p>', '43.8589079269445', '18.432360291481015', 'Hotel Old Sarajevo features elegant accommodation in the pedestrian zone of the old town of Sarajevo (Baščaršija).', 4764, '-226,-1,107', 1, 'Noćenje,Spavanje,Kreveti,Wi - Fi,TV Kablovska', 115, 19, '38', '0', 1, 0, 1, 1, 'hotel old sarajevo', 'nocenje,spavanje,kreveti,wi - fi,tv kablovska', 'hotel old sarajevo features elegant accommodation in the pedestrian zone of the old town of sarajevo (ba&scaron;car&scaron;ija).', 1, 'P