(150, 'Hacienda - Cantina Mexicana', 'hacienda-cantina-mexicana', 16, 147, '"Hacienda" Cantina Mexicana is a lounge bar and restaurant and in the content, special offers and style belongs to the category of highly rated restaurants. Through its four-year operation, "Hacienda" has acquired an enviable reputation, both among the citizens of Sarajevo, and the foreigners who live, work or visit our city. Because of its special restaurant menus, atmosphere, music, programs, etc., for the "Hacienda" is to say that has become a favorite place of the urban population of all generations, lovers of ethno cuisine, cocktails and wine.\r\nIn addition to a very rich offer the standard Mexican dishes and dessert, the excellent wines from all over the world, as well as an enviable selection of cocktails, "Hacienda" offers the possibility of special orders (Mediterranean, Italian, French cuisine). This restaurant has been allowed a FREE WIRELESS connection, as your time spent at the restaurant seems more comfortable and nice.\r\n\r\nSarajevo’s original cocktail bar, this lavish Mexican-themed enterprise in the centre of Baščaršija is a visual and relaxing retreat reminiscent of Seville or Guadalajara. Great cocktails such as Caipirinhas and Margaritas start at €4, as nocturnal Sarajevo descends to listen to Latin Jazz, Salsa and Cuban funk, see and be seen, dance and drink.', '43.85838574410204', '18.430150151252747', '"Hacienda" Cantina Mexicana is a lounge bar and restaurant and in the content, special offers and style belongs to the category of highly rated restaurants. ', 726, '-194,0,107', 1, 'Kafić,Kafa,Sok,Čaj,Koktel,Restoran,Meksicka kuhinja,Wi - Fi,Bašta', 462, 15, '3', '0', 1, 0, 1, 1, 'hacienda - cantina mexicana', 'kafic,kafa,sok,caj,koktel,restoran,meksicka kuhinja,wi - fi,basta', '"hacienda" cantina mexicana is a lounge bar and restaurant and in the content, special offers and style belongs to the category of highly rated restaurants. ', 1, 'Hacienda - Cantina Mexicana