(180, 'Mutvak', 'mutvak', 2, 1129, '<p>Mutvak is one of the best places to eat when you do not have to much time to spend in a classic restaurant. Mutvak operates as a fast food on two locations, both in city center. You will be surprised by variety of the food they offer. However, you should definitely not miss their most popular dish called "Kebab". Kebab refers to a variety of meat dishes in Pashtun,Turkish, Persian, Caucasian, Central Asian, South Asian and some of the African cuisines, consisting of grilled or broiled meats wrapped in Turkish bread accompanied by lettuce tomatoes with garlic sauce.<br><br>Mutvak is also one of those fast food restaurants offering a free home delivery. For more details we recommend you to visit their official web site, where you can provide insight in full menu list with prices included.<br></p>', '43.85608615117277', '18.408723324537277', 'Mutvak is one of the best places to eat when you do not have to much time to spend in a classic restaurant.', 4403, '-4,1,107', 1, 'Kebab,Pizza,Roštilj', 337, 13, '4', '0', 1, 0, 1, 1, 'mutvak', 'kebab,pizza,rostilj', 'mutvak is one of the best places to eat when you do not have to much time to spend in a classic restaurant.', 1, 'Mutvak', 'mutvak-en', '', '', 'mutvak', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
