(260, 'Divan', 'b', 38, 1209, 'Hotel Divan offers accommodation in Sarajevo.\r\n\r\nEach room has a TV. Some units have a seating area for your convenience. Certain rooms feature views of the mountains or city. Every room is fitted with a private bathroom. For your comfort, you will find slippers, free toiletries and a hair dryer.\r\n\r\nThere is a 24-hour front desk at the property.\r\n\r\nSebilj Fountain is 100 metres from Hotel Divan, while Bascarsija Street is 100 metres from the property. The nearest airport is Sarajevo Airport, 9 km from the property.', '43.86004124138001', '18.429699540138245', 'Hotel Divan offers accommodation in Sarajevo.', 380, '6,-8,107', 1, 'Noćenje,Prenočište,Smještaj,Doručak', 59, 19, '54', '0', 1, 0, 1, 1, 'b&b divan', 'nocenje,prenociste,smjestaj,dorucak', '', 1, 'B&B Divan', 'b-en', '', '', 'b&b divan', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
