(594, 'Dom Oružanih snaga BiH', 'dom_oruzanih_snaga_bih', 74, 801, '', '43.857283343083346', '18.42409372329712', '', 646, '-232,-17,107', 1, '', 330, 17, '2', '0', 1, 0, 1, 1, 'dom oruzanih snaga bih', '', '', 1, 'Officers’ Casino (Army Hall B&H)', 'dom_oruzanih_snaga_bih-en', '<p></p>The Officers’ Casino was built in 1881 according to Karl Pařík’s design.&nbsp;<div></div><div>The Officers’ Casino was built in 1881 according to Karl Pařík’s design.\n It was the core of Sarajevo’s social life in late 19th and early 20th \ncentury up until the construction of the Country House also known as the\n "Gentlemen''s Club”(present-day National Theatre). The Army Hall of \nBosnia and Herzegovina has been used by the military ever since its \nestablishment for various purposes. It holds two grand halls for \nreceptions and cultural events. This was the venue of the first military\n music concert (1881), numerous art exhibitions, public lectures...&nbsp;<br></div>', 'The Officers’ Casino was built in 1881 according to Karl Pařík’s design. ', 'officers’ casino (army hall b&h)', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
