(1065, 'Akademija likovnih umjetnosti Sarajevo', 'akademija-likovnih-umjetnosti-sarajevo', 36, 1296, '', '43.85589080740078', '18.417779803276062', 'Akademija likovnih umjetnosti Sarajevo, kao javna visokoškolska ustanova i članica Univerziteta Sarajevo', 1178, '-19,-13,107', 1, '', 1093, 15, '3', '0', 2, 0, 1, 1, 'akademija likovnih umjetnosti sarajevo', '', 'akademija likovnih umjetnosti sarajevo, kao javna visokoskolska ustanova i clanica univerziteta sarajevo', 1, 'Academy of Fine Arts (Evangelistic Church)', 'akademija-likovnih-umjetnosti-sarajevo-en', '<p></p>The Academy is located in the former Evangelistic Church, built by the \nEvangelistic Municipality in 1899 according to Karl Pařík’s design. This\n church portrays early Christian and Byzantium style.<div><br><div>The central domed edifice was redesigned in 1911, when the church wings \nwere added. The Academy of Fine Arts has moved into the building in \n1981.</div></div>', 'The Academy is located in the former Evangelistic Church, built by the Evangelistic Municipality in 1899 according to Karl Pařík’s design.', 'academy of fine arts (evangelistic church)', 'akademija likovnih umjetnosti sarajevo, kao javna visokoskolska ustanova i clanica univerziteta sarajevo', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00') ;
