(1235, 'Gazi Husrev-begova biblioteka', 'gazi-husrev-begova-biblioteka-gazi-husrevbegova-46', 90, 481, '', '43.859654447065786', '18.428471088409424', '', 2200, '119,-7,97', 1, 'Biblioteka,Čitaonice,Muzej', 206, 15, '46', '0', 1, 0, 1, 1, 'gazi husrev-begova biblioteka', 'biblioteka,citaonice,muzej', '', 1, 'Ghazi Husrev-Bey’s Library', 'gazi-husrev-begova-biblioteka-gazi-husrevbegova-46-en', '<p></p>Ghazi Husrev-Bey’s Library is a treasury of Oriental culture and wisdom,\n manuscripts and valuable books.It is a specialized Oriental library \npreserving scientific information about the cultural heritage, mainly \ndating back to the Ottoman period.&nbsp;<div>The library, thus, has represented a guardian of the economic and \ncultural history of Bosnia and Herzegovina for over 400 years. The \nlibrary fund holds over a hundred thousand books, manuscripts, various \nhistoric documents…&nbsp;</div>', 'Ghazi Husrev-Bey’s Library is a treasury of Oriental culture and wisdom, manuscripts and valuable books.', 'ghazi husrev-bey’s library', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
