(1601, 'Pansion River', 'pansion-river', 42, 158, '<p>Above the banks of the river Miljacka, located in a historic place of Bentbaša - Sarajevo Old Town, newly adapted luxury rooms and apartments in Guest House River offer chic and modern accommodation just 300 meters away from the Sarajevo City Hall - Viječnica, and famous Baščaršija Fountain. Olympic mountain Jahorina is 25 km away.<br><br>With stylish décor and comfortable large beds, each room has its own private bathroom, free Wi-Fi and flat-screen TV with satellite channels for guests to relax with. In most of the rooms, guests will have opportunity to enjoy drinking coffee on their own spacious terrace above the river, with breathtaking view of the lake, river, hills and Sarajevo Old Town. Free private parking is also provided in front of the Guest House.<br><br>The breakfast is served at our traditional restaurant ''Bazeni'' where Oscar winning actress, beautiful Penelope Cruz, was filming “Twice Born”, Sergio Castellitto’s movie.<br><br>Upon request, Pansion River offers free Airport Shuttle to its guests.<br><br>Feel the magical spirit of Sarajevo in a historic place of Bentbaša that is sung in many songs, including the old traditional song, by many the anthem of Sarajevo – “When I went to Bembaša, To Bembaša, to the river, I took a white lamb, A white lamb with me“, and let your trip to Sarajevo be remembered forever in your hearts.<br></p>', '43.86017661879717', '18.43745917081833', 'Above the banks of the river Miljacka, located in a historic place of Bentba&scaron;a - Sarajevo Old Town, newly adapted luxury rooms and apartments in Guest House River offer chic and modern accommodation just 300 meters away from the Sarajevo City Hall ', 4915, '181,0,107', 1, 'Pansion,Smještaj,Parking,Bašta,Restoran,Priroda,Voda,Wi - Fi,TV', 176, 14, 'bb', '0', 1, 0, 4, 1, 'pansion river', 'pansion,smjestaj,#parking,#basta,#restoran,#priroda,#voda,#wi - fi,#tv', 'above the banks of the river miljacka, located in a histori