(2471, 'Monument Club', 'monument-club', 29, 765, '<p><p></p><div><div><div><p>Jazz & Night Club, official partner of Jazz Fest Sarajevo, for more than 10 years. With the long list of bends and artists who perform on our Late Nite Stage through the solo concerts or jam sessions, we could proudly present our club as a hot spot for best jazz concerts in city for last couple of years. Our garden, as one of finest in the heart of Sarajevo, with the view on the city cathedral, is a must see&feel place in our town.</p></div></div></div><p></p><div><div><div><p>We are opened from 8 a.m. till after midnight. From November on, until April is a concert season, with live acts on Friday and Monday evenings. Great coffee, cold beer and beverages, with an excellent music selection, combined in an historical ambient of the location, make it Club Monument as a place for enjoying all sins. Welcome</p></div></div></div><br></p>', '43.85876674462706', '18.425507247447968', 'Jazz & Night Club, official partner of Jazz Fest Sarajevo, for more than 10 years.', 4740, '69,5,107', 1, 'Jazz,Zabava,Muzika uživo,Pivo,Kafić,Kafa,Alkohol', 622, 15, '3', '0', 1, 0, 1, 1, 'monument club', '#jazz,#zabava,#muzika uzivo,#pivo,#kafic,#kafa,#alkohol', 'jazz & night club, official partner of jazz fest sarajevo, for more than 10 years.', 2, 'Monument Club', 'monument-club-en', '<p><p></p><div><div><div><p>Jazz &amp; Night Club, official partner of Jazz Fest Sarajevo, for more than 10 years. With the long list of bends and artists who perform on our Late Nite Stage through the solo concerts or jam sessions, we could proudly present our club as a hot spot for best jazz concerts in city for last couple of years.&nbsp;Our garden, as one of finest in the heart of Sarajevo, with the view on the city cathedral, is a must see&amp;feel place in our town.</p></div></div></div><p></p><div><div><div><p>We are opened from 8 a.m. till after midnight. From November on, until April is a concert season, with live acts on