(3286, 'Turkuaz Cafe & Restaurant', 'turkuaz', 2, 237, '<p><p>Turkuaz is a friendly Turkish restaurant specialising in authentic Turkish cuisine which has been served in ottoman palaces for centuries. You will be looked after by friendly attentive staff and the Owner Ertu who appears the strong silent type but who is not without a sense of humour. Its affordable prices make it a great choice for a night out, a family lunch or business meeting.</p><p>The atmosphere is easy and laid back with an open serving area so you can see your food being cooked in the traditional wood stone oven or over the charcoal grills for that fantastic rustic flavour and the traditional Turkish music played in the background just adds to the ambiance.</p><p>Whatever the occasion Turkuaz is the perfect choice, from romantic dinners to lively celebrations, with a traditional belly dancer performing every Friday and Saturday night to add to the experience of the Middle East, if you want to give it a try you are welcome to put on the shimmy belt and join in, it’s harder than it looks but great fun.</p><p>We also have a function room upon request that can be booked for various occasions where you would like a more private evening but still with all the flavour of Turkey. It can seat around 20 people and is an informal cushioned space that makes you feel as if you are in your own living room</p><br></p>', '43.85900849496674', '18.432360291481015', 'Turkuaz is a friendly Turkish restaurant specialising in authentic Turkish cuisine which has been served in ottoman palaces for centuries.', 4764, '-92,-5,107', 1, '#Restoran,#Turska,#Wi - Fi,#Hrana,#Kafa,#Čaj', 191, 15, '23', '0', 1, 0, 3, 1, 'turkuaz cafe & restaurant', '', 'turkuaz is a friendly turkish restaurant specialising in authentic turkish cuisine which has been served in ottoman palaces for centuries.', 1, 'Turkuaz Cafe & Restaurant', 'turkuaz-en', '<p><p>Turkuaz is a friendly Turkish restaurant specialising in authentic Turkish cuisine wh