(3315, 'Restoran Casa United', 'restoran-casa-united', 2, 222, '<p><p><i>"Želite da vrijeme doručka, ručka ili večere provedete sa dragim osobama ili poslovnim partnerima, a uz to uživate u širokom izboru jela i pića, Casa United je restoran za vas.</i></p> <p><i>Doručak, u koji je uračunata neograničena konzumacija jela i pića sa švedskog stola, je u terminu od 08:00 do 12:00. Sa švedskog stola za doručak možete probati omlete, sireve, suhomesnate proizvode, razne namaze ili pahuljice.</i></p> <p><i>Gostima je tokom cijelog dana dostupan „a la carte“ meni sa specijalnim ponudama dana. Na jelovniku Casa Uniteda možete pronaći mesne ili riblje specijalitete, razne vrste Wok-ova, paste i rižota, pite, pice... Također, za sve obroke dostupne su supe, salate, svježe voće i povrće, deserti. Predah napravite uz kafu i druge tople napitke, a osvježite se uz neki od prirodnih ili gaziranih sokova.</i></p> <p><i>Moderno uređeni ambijent Casa Uniteda pruža toplinu i ugodnu atmosferu, a profesionalno osoblje potrudit će se da vam posjeta restoranu ostane u najboljem sjećanju.</i></p> <p><i>Casa United se nalazi u neposrednoj blizini Narodnog pozorišta i Bosanskog kulturnog centra."</i></p><br></p>', '43.85756571440875', '18.42190772294998', 'Želite da vrijeme doručka, ručka ili večere provedete sa dragim osobama ili poslovnim partnerima, a uz to uživate u širokom izboru jela i pića, Casa United je restoran za vas.', 4773, '-207,5,107', 1, 'Hrana,Italijanska kuhinja,Mediteranska kuhinja,Meksicka kuhinja,Nacionalna kuhinja,Doručak,Ručak', 260, 15, '22', '0', 1, 0, 4, 1, 'restoran casa united', '#hrana,#italijanska kuhinja,#mediteranska kuhinja,#meksicka kuhinja,#nacionalna kuhinja,#dorucak,#rucak', 'zelite da vrijeme dorucka, rucka ili vecere provedete sa dragim osobama ili poslovnim partnerima, a uz to uzivate u sirokom izboru jela i pica, casa united je restoran za vas.', 1, 'Restaurant Casa United', 'restoran-casa-united-en', '<p><p>If you''d like to have\nbreakfast, lunch or dinner with significant others or business associates and also\nenjoy a wide selection of food and drink, then Casa United is the restaurant\nfor you.</p>\n\n<p>Breakfast is available\nfrom 8:00 a.m. to 12:00 p.m. and includes an all-you-can-eat buffet. You can\ntry omelettes, cheeses, dried meats and different kinds of spreads and cereals.</p>\n\n<p>Casa United’s à la\ncarte menu is available the rest of the day with daily specials, such as meat\nand fish specialties, steaks and other main courses, various items from the\nwok, pastas, risotto, drinks…. There are also soups, salads, fresh fruits and\nvegetables and deserts to go with your meals. Have a break over coffee or\nanother warm beverage or enjoy some refreshing natural or carbonated juices.</p>\n\n<p>Casa United’s modern interior provides\na warm and pleasant atmosphere, and the professional staff will do their best\nto make sure your visit serves as a pleasant memory.</p>\n\n<p>Casa United is located close to the\nNational Theater and the Bosnian Cultural Center (BKC).</p><br></p>', 'If you''d like to have breakfast, lunch or dinner with significant others or business associates and also enjoy a wide selection of food and drink, then Casa United is the restaurant for you.', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
