(5147, 'Restoran Bazeni', 'restoran-bazeni', 2, 158, '<p><p>U predivnom ambijentu na obroncima rijeke Miljacke nalazi se poznati ugostiteljski objekat restoran „Bazeni“ sa dugogodišnjom tradicijom.</p> <p>Restoran raspolaže sa 250 udobnih mjesta, a uz restoran je i ljetna bašta uređena u bosanskom stilu sa pogledom na rijeku, stari grad, Vijećnicu, Alifakovac i mnoge druge sarajevske historijske znamenitosti koje pričaju lijepu sarajevsku priču punu ljubavi.</p> <p>Poznati smo po organizovanju svečanih ručkova, svadbi, novogodišnjih, bajramskih i sličnih manifestacija, a u našem restoranu su boravili i Oscarom nagrađivani glumci Penelope Cruz i Javier Bardem koji su snimali scene za film „Venuto al Mondo“, kao i ekipa filma „Nafaka“.</p> <p>2009. godine restoran „Bazeni“ je proglašen i za najbolji muzičko – ugostiteljski objekat u Bosni i Heregovini.</p> <p>Osoblje restorana „Bazeni“ raduje se Vašoj posjeti i želi Vam ugodan boravak u našem objektu i pratećim sadržajima.</p> <p>Utemeljeno 1988. god.</p></p>', '43.860074118781', '18.437318354845047', 'U predivnom ambijentu na obroncima rijeke Miljacke nalazi se poznatiugostiteljski objekat restoran &bdquo;Bazeni&ldquo; sa dugogodi&scaron;njom tradicijom.', 4910, '44,3,107', 1, 'Restoran,Bašta,Parking,Wi - Fi', 118, 14, 'bb', '0', 1, 0, 3, 1, 'restoran bazeni', 'restoran,basta,parking,wi - fi', 'u predivnom ambijentu na obroncima rijeke miljacke nalazi se poznatiugostiteljski objekat restoran „bazeni“ sa dugogodisnjom tradicijom.', 1, 'Restaurant Bazeni', 'restoran-bazeni-en', '<p align="left">Restaurant &bdquo;Bazeni&ldquo; is well known  restaurant in Sarajevo, located in the most beautiful part of the city, a  famous place called Bantbaša, with open terraces placed over the banks of the  Miljacka river, with a beautiful scenic view, surrounded by hills and river,  City Hall Vijećnica, Alifakovac and many other historical sites that tell a  beautiful Sarajevo story.</p>\n<p align="left">It has a large number of seats, over 200 of indoor and outdoor  space, and a parking place.</p>\n<p align="left">Restaurant is well known for organizing larger group arrivals,  business conferences, weddings, New Year''s Eve and Multicultural Holiday  celebrations with traditional live music. We have hosted many eminent  representatives of diplomacy in Bosnia, organizing events such as Independence  Day for the USA Embassy and French Embassy. The film scenes from the movie  &quot;Venuto al Mondo&quot; were filmed in our restaurant with Oscar winning  actress Penelope Cruz and her husband Javier Bardem, who were also our guests.</p>\n<p align="left">In 2009, restaurant &bdquo;Bazeni&ldquo; received an official Oscar  Popularity Award for the best music restaurant in Bosnia and Herzegovina.</p>\n<p align="left">We look forward to your visit and wish you a  pleasant stay in our guest house and other facilities. </p>\n<p align="left">Founded in  1988</p>', 'Restaurant Bazeni is well known restaurant in Sarajevo, located in the most beautiful part of the city, a famous place called Bantbaš', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
