(5213, 'FinConf 2016', 'finconf-2016', 99, 1834, '<p><p></p><div><div><div><h3>WHO WE ARE</h3><div><p>FinConf is the premier regional&nbsp;conference platform dedicated to innovation in financial services.</p><p>FinConf aims at providing a forum for open and forward oriented discussion of European Financial, Regulatory &amp; Banking services.and trends.</p><p>Leading topics, high-level speakers and top decision-makers share insights with technology partners&nbsp;and collaborate focusing on various&nbsp;and complex line-ups to rethink financial services.</p><a href=''http://finconf.com/''></a><p></p></div></div></div></div><p></p><div><div><div><h3>WHAT WE DO</h3><div><p>We structure our events by investigating into market challenges and top issues that industries&nbsp;endure to render the most effective learning and networking platforms by creating impactful and&nbsp;pragmatic B2B conferences.</p><p>Being customer focused and having our client’s priorities in mind are among our core values and&nbsp;essential to the way we operate our business.</p><p>We are devoted to deliver distinctive and comprehensive events and striving to maintain the highest&nbsp;qualities and standards.</p><a href=''http://finconf.com/#''></a><p></p></div></div></div></div><p></p><div><div><div><h3>WHY FINCONF</h3><div><p>At our 2nd Annual Conference dedicated to innovation in financial services your company shall benchmark advanced strategies, gain the&nbsp;latest knowledge and a competitive edge while enjoying a 5 star environment.</p><p>We cordially invite you to meet &amp; greet your peers to discuss the current challenges and future Financial, Regulatory &amp; Banking services and trends.</p></div></div></div></div><br></p>', '43.82415539217691', '18.308471739292145', 'FinConf is the premier regional conference platform dedicated to innovation in financial services.', 4928, '-307,5,107', 1, 'Ekonomija,Wi - Fi', 41, 14, '3a', '0', 1, 0, 1, 1, 'finconf 2016', '#ekonomija,#wi - fi', 'finconf is the premier regional conference platform dedicated to innovation in financial services.', 1, 'FinConf 2016', 'finconf-2016-en', '<p><p></p><div><div><div><h3>WHO WE ARE</h3><div><p>FinConf is the premier regional&nbsp;conference platform dedicated to innovation in financial services.</p><p>FinConf aims at providing a forum for open and forward oriented discussion of European Financial, Regulatory &amp; Banking services.and trends.</p><p>Leading topics, high-level speakers and top decision-makers share insights with technology partners&nbsp;and collaborate focusing on various&nbsp;and complex line-ups to rethink financial services.</p><a href="http://finconf.com/"></a><p></p></div></div></div></div><p></p><div><div><div><h3>WHAT WE DO</h3><div><p>We structure our events by investigating into market challenges and top issues that industries&nbsp;endure to render the most effective learning and networking platforms by creating impactful and&nbsp;pragmatic B2B conferences.</p><p>Being customer focused and having our client’s priorities in mind are among our core values and&nbsp;essential to the way we operate our business.</p><p>We are devoted to deliver distinctive and comprehensive events and striving to maintain the highest&nbsp;qualities and standards.</p><a href="http://finconf.com/#"></a><p></p></div></div></div></div><p></p><div><div><div><h3>WHY FINCONF</h3><div><p>At our 2nd Annual Conference dedicated to innovation in financial services your company shall benchmark advanced strategies, gain the&nbsp;latest knowledge and a competitive edge while enjoying a 5 star environment.</p><p>We cordially invite you to meet &amp; greet your peers to discuss the current challenges and future Financial, Regulatory &amp; Banking services and trends.</p></div></div></div></div><br></p>', 'FinConf is the premier regional conference platform dedicated to innovation in financial services.', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
